metadata.name: 'Bull Market' 2022
metadata.description:
'Bull Market' is my Genesis on FND, and is a mixture of Digital Painting, Photography and 3D elements. I use layers of photographs, scanned textures and bold graphics to create Urban Surreal Landscapes. I am mainly inspired by the work of William Turner, WK Interact, Alexander Calder, and my everyday experiences IRL and online.
